oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Apple butter making
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Photograph of apple butter being made at Fred Matherty's home located in Old Butler, Tennessee. The apple butter is being made for Baptist Children's Home, and orphanage, based in Nashville.
